title: Olympic diver Tom Daley engaged to Dustin Lance Black
text:
Olympic diver Tom Daley engaged to Dustin Lance Black Bronze-medal winner announces engagement on Instagram Author: By Lisa Respers France CNN Published On: 2 h Updated 12 m (CNN) - 
Olympic diver Tom Daley is officially off the market. 
The bronze-medal winner announced via Instagram that he is now engaged to his boyfriend of two years, Academy Award-winning screenwriter Dustin Lance Black. 
"#HeSaidYES and then #ISaidYES Thanks for all the lovely messages!" says the caption on a photo of their rings and a newspaper announcement of their engagement. Quick Clicks
